JNDI Name: jdbc/Park
Persistence unit name: JpaPUPark
Table generate strategi: Drop and Table
pool name: derby-park

Persistence Provider: EclipseLink ( JPA2.1 )

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
List the parks
GET
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add new park
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/addpark
{   
	"name":"FantasticPark",
        "postCode":"1098",
        "country":"HUN",
        "city":"Budapest",
        "street":"Fo utca",
        "streetNumber":"34",
        "money":123456,
        "area":1000
}
<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add new machine
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/machine/addmachine
{
	"fantasiaName":"SuperGokart",
	"sizeOfMachine":"400",
	"priceOfTicket":"500",
	"capacity":"30",
	"type":"GOKART",
	"minimumAge":"14"
}

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add machine to park
Verify that the id of park and machine is valid
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/2/addmachine/1
The first the park id and the second is the machine id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Remove machine	//teszt
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/2/removemachine/1
The first the park id and the second is the machine id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add visitor
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/addvisitor
{
	"name":"TestVisitor",
	"state":"REST",
	"entryDate":12000,
	"age":18,
	"isActive":"false"
}
<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Get visitors
GET
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor


<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Login visitor to park
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/logintopark/1
Verify that the id of visitor is valid

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Exit visitor from park
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/exitfrompark/1
Verify that the id of visitor is valid









